
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Example 1</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" media="all" />
  <style type="text/css">

    a {
      color: #5D6975;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    p {
      text-align: center
    }

    body {
      position: relative;
      width: 21cm;
      height: 29.7cm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      color: #001028;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-family: Arial;
    }

    header {
      padding: 10px 0;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    h1 {
      border-top: 1px solid  #5D6975;
      border-bottom: 1px solid  #5D6975;
      color: #5D6975;
      font-size: 2.4em;
      line-height: 1.4em;
      font-weight: normal;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      background: url(dimension.png);
    }

    #user {
      float: left;
    }

    #user span, #driver span {
      color: #5D6975;
      text-align: right;
      width: 52px;
      margin-right: 10px;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.8em;
    }

    #driver {
      float: right;
      text-align: left;
    }




    footer {
      color: #5D6975;
      width: 100%;
      height: 30px;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #C1CED9;
      padding: 8px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Contract ID: 30</h1>
    <p>
      The following is a transport covenant concluded between the following parties in common agreement of:
      <strong>Time: </strong><%= @travel.time %>
      <strong>Distance: </strong><%= @travel.distance %>
      <strong>Value: </strong><%= @travel.value %>
    </p>
    <div id="user">
      <h3>User</h3>
      <div><span>CC</span> <%= @travel.user_identification %></div>
      <div><span>PHONE</span> <%= @travel.user_phone %></div>
      <div><span>EMAIL</span> <a href="#{@travel.user_email}"><%= @travel.user_email %></a></div>
    </div>
    <div id="driver">
      <h3>Driver</h3>
      <div><span>CC</span> <%= @travel.user.owner_identification %></div>
      <div><span>PHONE</span> <%= @travel.user.owner_phone %></div>
      <div><span>EMAIL</span> <a href="#{@travel.user.email}"><%= @travel.user.email %></a></div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <footer>
    Contract was created on a computer and is valid without the signature and seal.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
